      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 testing was conducted at a single standard load offset (5 mm eccentricity) under ambient laboratory conditions. Temperature and humidity were logged throughout each test session and remained within acceptable ranges. The protocol is the recognized industry standard for this device class, and all eleven constructs were tested under identical, well-controlled conditions at two accredited facilities. Minor inter-laboratory variability was within expected bounds and did not affect outcome interpretation."
